---
title: Chermoula Yoghurt Chicken & Roast Veggie Couscous for Dinner with a Chicken & Roast Kumara Salad for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new twist on the recipe to create something different for lunch the next day! Combine our popular chermoula spice mix with yoghurt for a tasty marinade that keeps chicken strips tasty and tender over a bed of fragrant couscous and veggies. At lunch, transform it into a colourful roast kumara salad with creamy feta for a guaranteed flavour sensation.

